  <bioghist id="aspace_3557d37461c321e835c26de7959c015a">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Professor Emeritus of Geological Sciences, Cornell University.</p><p> George A. Kiersch received a B.S. from the Colorado School of Mines, and a Ph.D. from the University of Arizona. As well as teaching at Cornell, he worked as a geologist and exploration manager for industrial firms and government agencies and as a national and international consultant.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_74903ed9bd47b2c9cb6718631a17ce70">
